{"tid":1300413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12分鐘了解社會信用評分系統","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:53:28.000Z","uid":37554,"like":117,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"ca74daa85ba4589fa6f381c88af0d57e3c9b8213","tid":1300413,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"《視點31》【中國式‧信用】<br />\n近年中國各地政府推行社會信用評級，要求各部門以至企業，向中央平台集中推送個人或企業的「守信」和「失信」資料，建立「紅名單」及「黑名單」，再加以聯合獎懲。預計2020年，這套全國社會信用系統將基本建設完成，並應用在14億中國人的生活當中。<br />\n<br />\n《視點31》訪問了十年前率先推行信用評分系統的江蘇徐州睢寧縣，了解政策背後的目的和實際操作。當國家機構負起判斷民眾誠信高低之責，會利用甚麼樣的標準、尺度衡量？一個人或企業的信用狀況，對他的生活有何影響？社會是否變得更有誠信，還是變成一個全面監控的「奧威爾式」制度？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthk31thisweek/videos/433588127211768/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frthk31thisweek%2Fvideos%2F433588127211768%2F&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7CC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=ffa3b7f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthk31thisweek/videos/433588127211768/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSf4wgi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSf4wgi.png&h=37a19c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nKuH2n8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKuH2n8.png&h=4bcc06d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DFj4BO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DFj4BO.png&h=f2250661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6JE4BW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6JE4BW.png&h=1b605c89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28c77c889379bd326e354fb406cb9b291eaaf2dd","tid":1300413,"uid":37554,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"《視點31》【黑鏡人生‧淪落失信人】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srcGtNTMWvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsrcGtNTMWvs&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7CC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=8209d8fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srcGtNTMWvs</a><br />\n中國過去十年建構全國社會信用體系，收集得來的生活數據，用來評價民眾誠信。<br />\n據最新公布，全國已有近1400萬人被評為失信，社會上寸步難行；內地多以「老賴」形容他們，除了欠債不還老賴賬，「失信人」何以失信、遭遇如何？<br />\n編導:利君雅 張潔茵"},{"pid":"5cc555d6546e3e79b4b60854b8d10a8b9d640657","tid":1300413,"uid":37554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"視點31：逃犯條例；內地錄像監控；香港應用生物辨識技術<br />\n【新疆監控通道曝光，監控趨勢延伸本港？】內地超過一億的鏡頭鋪天蓋地形成監控網絡，部份鏡頭更具備人工智能，可以即時收集、儲存3D人面數據，準確辨認一個人的身份。北京一間科技公司表示，透過天眼和監控儀器，他們正在為新疆全省建立一個省級的「3D人像數據庫」。器材甚至可以收集每個人獨一無二的手機資料，方便追蹤和監控。公司又透露，他們的3D人臉識別技術亦應用在港珠澳大橋香港口岸，相關監控科技會否延伸香港？<br />\n(採訪：利君雅、張潔茵)<br />\n<br />\n【香港應用生物辨識科技】內地科技發展一日千里，香港近年亦大講創科，科技應用生活的同時，如何平衡應用需要與個人資料的擷取?香港對採集生物特徵方面的個人資料，又有否足夠保障？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4GYM2_T5-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW4GYM2_T5-A&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7CC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=0d0c97c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4GYM2_T5-A</a>"},{"pid":"fabff8d4f19d28e8d49dc7c75be73996f9cfa91b","tid":1300413,"uid":54511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"推推 呢個 再明d <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdgfCYK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdgfCYK.gif&h=5f085f0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e8d25cd431dd9211af9d79405d7f9d2f86eb110","tid":1300413,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"【九大訴求】陳同佳案，醫管局 唔可以不了了之<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300409</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25a25417738162ac3f03fb391d076331a7487a6b","tid":1300413,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: